00:17:07,234 --> 00:17:08,610
akan meninggalkan kota.

237
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:20,998
Begitu.

238
00:17:22,583 --> 00:17:23,417
Katja.

239
00:17:26,295 --> 00:17:27,212
Maukah kau...

240
00:17:28,505 --> 00:17:29,423
ikut denganku?

241
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,558
Naik kapal?

242
00:17:47,316 --> 00:17:49,026
Jangan bicara terlalu banyak.

243
00:17:50,152 --> 00:17:51,528
Nanti lidahmu tergigit.

244
00:18:23,852 --> 00:18:27,022
Indah sekali! Terima kasih banyak!

245
00:18:27,606 --> 00:18:29,233
Akan kutambahkan ke dinding.

246
00:18:29,942 --> 00:18:30,901
Juga, Takita.

247
00:18:31,401 --> 00:18:32,319
Berikan lenganmu.

248
00:18:34,988 --> 00:18:36,406
Gelang dari potongan naga.

249
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:41,370
Juga, balsam dari lendir
naga Salamandra mungil.

250
00:18:43,455 --> 00:18:44,832
Bisa menyembuhkan luka.

251
00:18:47,251 --> 00:18:49,795
Terima kasih, Nanami!

252
00:18:52,965 --> 00:18:54,550
Kembalilah.

253
00:18:57,052 --> 00:18:59,137
Kita akan pergi! Naiklah!

254
00:18:59,555 --> 00:19:03,058
- Ya, Pak.
- Jaga diri kalian.

255
00:19:03,392 --> 00:19:06,812
Dagingnya akan siap saat kalian kembali.

256
00:19:06,895 --> 00:19:08,939
Sisakan untukku!

257
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:15,028
Kembali ke langit.

258
00:19:15,112 --> 00:19:17,155
Itu artinya langit kekasih kita.

259
00:19:17,823 --> 00:19:19,658
- Sayangnya.
- Apa-apaan?

260
00:19:20,868 --> 00:19:23,162
Aku juga harus pergi.

261
00:19:23,871 --> 00:19:25,080
Dah, Katja.

262
00:19:31,837 --> 00:19:32,921
Giraud.

263
00:19:34,131 --> 00:19:35,632
Katja.

264
00:19:41,388 --> 00:19:42,556
Akan kupotong rambutmu.

265
00:19:43,557 --> 00:19:45,726
Kau terlihat seperti perempuan.

266
00:19:46,143 --> 00:19:47,811
Lima menit saja.

267
00:19:48,186 --> 00:19:49,771
Bisa ambilkan seprai dan gunting?

268
00:19:50,731 --> 00:19:52,107
Kurasa ada di kapal.

269
00:19:52,608 --> 00:19:53,442
Vannie!

270
00:19:54,693 --> 00:19:56,236
Bisa pinjam guntingmu?

271
00:19:57,362 --> 00:19:58,363
Akan kukembalikan.

272
00:20:00,699 --> 00:20:03,035
Ya, santai saja.

273
00:20:08,832 --> 00:20:10,000
Aku senang kita bertemu.

274
00:20:12,794 --> 00:20:13,795
Jaga dirimu.

275
00:20:43,742 --> 00:20:44,868
Tiga tahun...

276
00:20:45,077 --> 00:20:45,953
Astaga,

277
00:20:46,286 --> 00:20:48,497
kau masih memikirkan itu, Mika?

278
00:20:48,872 --> 00:20:50,582
Bersemangatlah.

279
00:20:52,793 --> 00:20:54,962
Mika, saatnya berjaga.

280
00:20:58,006 --> 00:20:59,132
Giraud?

281
00:21:02,010 --> 00:21:03,178
Apa yang terjadi?

282
00:21:04,137 --> 00:21:05,430
Siapa yang peduli?

283
00:21:06,098 --> 00:21:08,308
Aku di depan, kau di belakang.

284
00:21:09,601 --> 00:21:12,020
- Giraud!
- Takita.

285
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:14,856
Semua orang punya alasan.

286
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:16,400
Bahkan lelaki.

287
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:18,277
Aku di depan.

288
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:21,238
- Tidak, aku.
- Tidak, aku.

289
00:21:22,072 --> 00:21:23,657
Tidak, aku!

290
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:25,033
- Aku yang di depan.
- Aku!

291
00:21:25,117 --> 00:21:26,410
- Aku!
- Aku!

292
00:21:26,493 --> 00:21:28,161
- Aku di depan!
- Tidak, aku!

293
00:21:28,245 --> 00:21:30,998
- Aku di depan.
- Kenapa kau harus di depan?

294
00:21:31,081 --> 00:21:32,124
Silakan saja.

